{"tid":2446541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[真係射上moon]  科學家準備670萬精子樣本 計畫「射到月球上」避免世界滅亡","createTime":"2021-03-14T13:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T11:20:56.000Z","uid":141151,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"eaeecbdf3f6a2e73d05ac4c4f6f97910e22cafa5","tid":2446541,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:47:43.000Z","msg":"科學家準備670萬精子樣本 計畫「射到月球上」避免世界滅亡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99670%E8%90%AC%E7%B2%BE%E5%AD%90%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC-%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%B0%84%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%88%E7%90%83%E4%B8%8A-%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%BB%85%E4%BA%A1-011743681.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599670%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E6%259C%25AC-%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%2595%25AB-%25E5%25B0%2584%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%2590%2583%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E9%2581%25BF%25E5%2585%258D%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%25BB%2585%25E4%25BA%25A1-011743681.html&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=0a91754d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99670%E8%90%AC%E7%B2%BE%E5%AD%90%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC-%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%B0%84%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%88%E7%90%83%E4%B8%8A-%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%BB%85%E4%BA%A1-011743681.html</a><br />\n<br />\n近日有科學家建議，人類可以建造一個裝有670萬精子、卵子樣本的「現代方舟」，接著將這個方舟射向月球保存。此舉的最重要的目的就是，即便人類面臨了世界末日，透過這個方舟保存的精子與卵子，也能讓地球「重新啟動」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《Insider》報導指出，有6名美國亞利桑那大學的研究人員提出一個構想，他們認為地球天災人禍不斷，為了人類之後的發展，必須要準備一套「地球保險計畫」。這套計畫的主要目標，就是收集地球上動物的精子、卵子，植物的種子，甚至是孢子，共計670萬份。將這些生物樣本存放在太空船中，接著把這個太空船射向月球，讓太空船可以以備份庫的形式存放在月球上。<br />\n<br />\n而存放在月球的哪裡，這群研究人員也有他們的想法，他們表示，目前在月球表面發現了200多個因為早期月球火山爆發而產生的地下洞穴，透過儀器分析，裡面最寬的地下洞穴寬達5公里，長達數百公里，裡面溫度恆定，而且可以讓宇宙射線無法穿透，是個非常適合存放方舟太空船的地方。<br />\n<br />\n其實現在在地球上有個類似的設施，那就是位於挪威瓦爾巴群島的「種子庫」，裡面存放了全球100多萬份植物的樣本。研究人員Jekan Thangavelautham也表示，根據他們的計算，只要250次的飛行，就能夠完成670萬生物樣本的寄送，評估下來是個很可行的方式。"},{"pid":"5e69a0906821210c78033d6c3c80e03c9ccc1e69","tid":2446541,"uid":66365,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"放啲甲由上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71b30d1cbea9eba93c02d45598b8133176641fc","tid":2446541,"uid":60831,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"仲緊要冇支那人同黑人嘅精子"},{"pid":"561edd0bfded10f431024f2a00b152486ae9c8a0","tid":2446541,"uid":36455,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"to the moon<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e99a858e049350132dcb84e9d36a55b8bc5f264","tid":2446541,"uid":77196,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"c71b30d1cbea9eba93c02d45598b8133176641fc","tid":2446541,"uid":60831,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"仲緊要冇支那人同黑人嘅精子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"美國科學家，應該全部都係黑人精同卵了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006d9fdc78e7123a4e70717621e283ead96b5840","tid":2446541,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea462a6a0b0adf145d8914453361dab3f066766","tid":2446541,"uid":170335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"火星異種ready"},{"pid":"ac13f2bf93d724f9df5164c230d24fd6ae2d51ab","tid":2446541,"uid":340729,"li